verses.roman:
jaya jaya jaya śrī-advaita ācārya
jaya jaya śrī-caitanya, nityānanda ārya

synonyms: jaya jaya—all glories; jaya—all glories; śrī-advaita ācārya—to Śrī Advaita Ācārya; jaya jaya—all glories; śrī-caitanya—to Lord Śrī Caitanya Mahāprabhu; nityānanda—Lord Nityānanda; ārya—the superior.
translation: All glories, all glories to Śrī Advaita Ācārya! All glories to Lord Caitanya Mahāprabhu and the superior Lord Nityānanda!
